USAGE="Usage: ${bold}pkg [--ask|--force] man PKGNAME${endcolour}

View the man pages in the given package.

NOTE: PKGNAME will be downloaded if needed, then
it's contents are searched for man pages.

The 'man' command will be used to view any man
pages found.

If multiple man pages exist in a package, all
will be loaded.

Packages are downloaded to $WORKDIR. Use -f to
force re-download of an existing package.

Use --ask to ask before downloading.
"
